     F** EAAR40 **********************************
     F* CREATE AOSHO INSTRUCTION TAG PUBLICATION DETAILS LIST
     F*               TV INPUT                 *
     F* C:N.HAYAKAWA            1988.05.08       *
     F***CALL EAAC40 FOR TEST****14***************
     FEAAWP41 IP  F     200            DISK
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGADPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FQPRINT  O   F     198     OF     PRINTER
     IEAAWP41 AA  01
     I                                        1   1 RKBNM
     I                                        2   2 SKJYM
     I                                        3   60TOKUM
